trans-unit.source: Provides a thread-safe list of <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en sikker liste over <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceListener"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The TraceListenerCollection list is used to specify the output listeners for the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collections.
trans-unit.target: Listen TraceListenerCollection brukes til å angi utdata lyttere for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlinger.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Trace.Listeners%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You cannot create an instance of this class.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ikke opprette en forekomst av denne klassen.

trans-unit.source: This list is thread-safe, however the methods used to access the list and the enumerator do not take synchronization locks.
trans-unit.target: Denne listen er sikker, men metodene for tilgang til listen og enumeratoren ikke trer i synkronisering låser.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the collection is copied, the copy is modified, and a reference is set to the copy of the collection.
trans-unit.target: I stedet samlingen kopieres kopien endres og er angitt en referanse til kopien av samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Methods like <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Remove%2A>, and <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceListenerCollection.Clear%2A> modify the elements in the collection.
